data.description: This peaceful, quiet 74+ acres can be used for so many things! The home sits on a knoll surrounded by trees and is very quiet. . There are beautiful views with plenty of room for horses, cattle or recreational vehicles of any kind. There is a large barn at the top of the first tax lot. The second tax lot is vacant. The two tax lots cannot be split which makes for one large beautiful property on which to live out your dreams and create your own paradise - whatever that may be!
